title: Hotlanta and cold Teresa!!!
description: Casey and Danielle are joined by their hilarious parasocial friend Mitra Jouhari (Three Busy Debras) to celebrate the new season of Atlanta, complete with new businesses, new peaches and old horrible husbands. Plus She by Sheree is back, how lucky are we to be alive right now? They also talk Ultimate Girls Trip 2 and Dial-up face-lifts, along with Tre's abandonment of Dolores and how personally we took it. It's a jam packed episode. ROLL THE TAPE!!!
